org.ow2.proactive.scheduler.common

Enum SchedulerEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<SchedulerEvent>
      • org.ow2.proactive.scheduler.common.SchedulerEvent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<SchedulerEvent>

    @PublicAPI
public enum SchedulerEvent
extends Enum<SchedulerEvent>
    Enumeration of all different events that scheduler can invoke.

    This is also used to choose which events you want to received from the scheduler.

    Since:
    ProActive Scheduling 0.9
    See Also:
    for more details. $Id$
